          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price is from the year 2017. The price is estimated as a proxy based on the source: https://farmdoc.illinois.edu/assets/management/machinery-costs/field_operations_2017.pdf. The prices were adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01). It was assumed that the global price is equal to the US price.</comment>
